3. Core Operators of Pantheon Geometry

3.1 Vector Operations
	•	dot product → alignment
	•	cross product → off-axis creativity
	•	projection → focus
	•	normalization → emotional clarity

3.2 Matrix Operations
	•	multiplication → transformation
	•	eigenvectors → stable attractors
	•	rotation matrices → frame switching
	•	reflection → Mirror daemon logic

3.3 Tensor Operations
	•	outer product → idea synthesis
	•	contraction → compression
	•	slicing → story extraction
	•	curvature → narrative stress detection

3.4 Geometric Operators
	•	gradient → direction of steepest meaning
	•	divergence → entropy leakage
	•	curl → emotional turbulence
	•	laplacian → clarity/rest state (Bombadil)

